attributes.review: First of all, I downloaded this app for the plain and simple respect that I have for Donald Trump as I’ve always wanted to be just like him. I started downloading this app on Tuesday, June 2nd and it literally JUST finished today, July 9th. That’s ridiculous. For the several weeks I was waiting, I took my pet rock for several walks and hand trimmed my grass with my fingernail clippers, I came periodically to check on the app progress and it still wasn’t done. I then proceeded to bring the weekly food down to the basement for my grandma and watered my rug. It finally finished and I decided that Donald Trump is just too good of a person to even be in the presence of an app, therefore giving the one-star rating.
